###

### Criar usuário
POST {{host}}/api/usuarios
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "novo@teste.com",
  "senha": "123456"
}

### Editar usuário
PUT {{host}}/api/usuarios/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "atualizado@teste.com",
  "senha": "654321"
}

### Deletar usuário
DELETE {{host}}/api/usuarios/1

@host = https://localhost:7270

### Criar reserva (válida: jantar 19–22h)
POST {{host}}/api/reservas
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usuarioId": 1,
  "mesaId": 1,
  "dataHora": "2025-10-01T19:30:00"
}

### Obter por id
GET {{host}}/api/reservas/1

### Listar por data
GET {{host}}/api/reservas?data=2025-10-01

### Listar todas
GET {{host}}/api/reservas

### Cancelar
DELETE {{host}}/api/reservas/1

### Pagar pedido (PIX) — aprovado
POST {{host}}/api/payments/process
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pedidoId": 1,
  "metodo": "pix",
  "valor": 99.90
}

### Pagar pedido com valor inválido — recusado
POST {{host}}/api/payments/process
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pedidoId": 1,
  "metodo": "cartao",
  "valor": 0
}
